BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:event_313453957@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260310T015215Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260312T183000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260312T230000
SUMMARY:Play Board Games at the Geekery
DESCRIPTION:Triangle Board Games and Bars\nCome play games at Gamers Geekery and Tavern every thursday night!\n\nStarting time is 6:30\, but feel free to come in anytime and just hang out for the night. Group is very casual and friendly.\n\nHow it works:\nCome on in\, grab a name tag and pay the $2.50 meetup participant fee at the bar area\, find the tables that are reserved for the Meetup group\, play games with others who show up. Food and drinks are available at the bar.\n\nPlease RSVP by noon day of. If less than four people are able to attend a given Wednesday the event will be canceled.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/triangle-board-games-and-bars/events/313453957/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260221T002708Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260221T002708Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/d/0/0/0/600_530993248.jpeg
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:event_313701066@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260310T015215Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260314T130000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260314T150000
SUMMARY:Euchre or cards
DESCRIPTION:Triangle Board Games and Bars\nThis is a regular Euchre and card meetup the 2nd and 4 Saturday afternoons.\nThe location is Geekery and Tavern in McGregor in Village. There is a bar with drinks and food\, we ask that you support them and there is a $10 table fee but we can stay and play all day. We will split the fee by 4 so $2.50 a person. The $2.50 fee can be paid to the venue by talking to any of the bartenders.\nBeginners are always welcome. We can't grow if we don't teach new players! Let me know if you want to help organize when I am out.\nBefore we get even 4s\, we will play other card games like The Crew or Seers Catalog. Also might play Tichu if there is enough interest.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/triangle-board-games-and-bars/events/313701066/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260308T213912Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260308T213912Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/b/e/1/600_533103041.jpeg
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:event_313287248@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260310T015215Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260317T183000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260317T200000
SUMMARY:Cary Jaycees Monthly General Membership Meeting 
DESCRIPTION:Triangle Board Games and Bars\nThe are Cary Jaycees\, your local crew of young professionals who know how to blend community service with a whole lot of fun. If you’ve ever wanted to meet awesome people\, make a real impact\, or build your leadership skills while doing some seriously cool projects\, this is your group. Some of our regular attendees don’t RSVP so please don’t be discouraged if others haven’t RSVPd\n\nThe Jaycees are always looking for new members\, so if you’ve been thinking about getting more involved in Cary and beyond\, consider this your sign. The Jaycees are an 18-40 year old group but we welcome everyone to be an alumni member (poorly named as you don't need to be a past member.) We meet on the third Tuesday of every month at Gamers Geekery and Tavern at 6:30 PM and would love for you to stop by\, say hello\, and see what they’re all about. We cover the game fee for anyone playing with us and will also have appetizers to share.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/triangle-board-games-and-bars/events/313287248/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260209T234259Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260209T234259Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/a/e/0/e/600_489584558.jpeg
END:VEVENT
